prompt:
Please create a list of 1 ideas for types of synthetic tabular data, with descriptions for the data they would contain, and what they might be useful for. Each dataset should be at least somewhat related to the COVID-19 pandemic.

Each item in the list should follow this format:
* [Name of the dataset] Data: This dataset would contain [description for the data it contains]. It could be used to [what it might be useful for].
response_text: 1. COVID-19 Vaccine Rollout Data: This dataset would contain detailed information about the rollout of COVID-19 vaccines, including when and where they were administered, who received them, and how effective they have been in preventing the spread of the virus. It could be used to track vaccine distribution trends and measure the effectiveness of different approaches to vaccine rollout.
